# textdomain: vlf_daylight_detector
Daylight Sensor=日光感測器
Provides redstone power when in sunlight=
Can be inverted=
Daylight detectors are redstone components which provide redstone power when they are in sunlight and no power otherwise. They can also be inverted.=
In inverted state, they provide redstone power when they are not in sunlight and no power otherwise.=
Use the daylight detector to toggle its state.=
Inverted Daylight Sensor=反相日光感測器
